name: s_m_Addr_From_Addr_Stg
description: Session pushed from PC to ICS : s_m_Addr_From_Addr_Stg

parameters.name: $Src_addr$
parameters.label: DBConnection_SRCM

runtimeAttrs.Sql Override:
select
	addr.SystemId,
	addr.ParentId,
	addr.CMMContainer,
	addr.Id,
	addr.AddrTypeCd,
	addr.Addr1,
	addr.Addr2,
	addr.Addr3,
	addr.Addr4,
	addr.City,
	addr.StateProvCd,
	addr.PostalCode,
	addr.County,
	addr.RegionCd,
	addr.RegionISOCd,
	addr.PreDirectional,
	addr.PrimaryNumber,
	addr.StreetName,
	addr.Suffix,
	addr.PostDirectional,
	addr.SecondaryDesignator,
	addr.SecondaryNumber,
	addr.VerificationMsg,
	addr.VerificationHash,
	addr.Latitude,
	addr.Longitude,
	addr.Score,
	addr.PrimaryNumberSuffix,
	addr.DPV,
	addr.DPVDesc,
	addr.DPVNotes,
	addr.DPVNotesDesc,
	addr.Attention,
	addr.BarcodeDigits,
	addr.CarrierRoute,
	addr.CongressCode,
	addr.CountyCode,
	addr.AdditionalLegal,
	addr.Section,
	addr.Township,
	addr.Lot,
	addr.Range,
	addr.Addition,
	addr.Block,
	addr.LegalDesc,
	addr.TownshipDir,
	addr.RangeDir,
	addr.Validated,
	addr.PrimaryMeridian,
	addr.PLSSCounty,
	addr.AddressHash,
	addr.GeocodeLevel,
	addr.GeocodeLevelDescription,
	addr.Meridian,
	addr.AddressOverrideInd,
	addr.DistanceToCoast,
	addr.DistanceToCoastInd,
	addr.AddrAliasModifiedInd,
	addr.Country
from
	addr addr
	 where
	addr.CmmContainer in ('Policy', 'Claim', 'Application')
	and ( AddrTypeCd like '%Mailing%'
		or AddrTypeCd like '%Risk%'
		or AddrTypeCd like '%CoverageStreetAddr%')

parameters.customQuery:
SELECT addr.SystemId, addr.ParentId, addr.CMMContainer, addr.Id, addr.AddrTypeCd, addr.Addr1, addr.Addr2, addr.Addr3, addr.Addr4, addr.City, addr.StateProvCd, addr.PostalCode, addr.County, addr.RegionCd, addr.RegionISOCd, addr.PreDirectional, addr.PrimaryNumber, addr.StreetName, addr.Suffix, addr.PostDirectional, addr.SecondaryDesignator, addr.SecondaryNumber, addr.VerificationMsg, addr.VerificationHash, addr.Latitude, addr.Longitude, addr.Score, addr.PrimaryNumberSuffix, addr.DPV, addr.DPVDesc, addr.DPVNotes, addr.DPVNotesDesc, addr.Attention, addr.BarcodeDigits, addr.CarrierRoute, addr.CongressCode, addr.CountyCode, addr.AdditionalLegal, addr.Section, addr.Township, addr.Lot, addr.Range, addr.Addition, addr.Block, addr.LegalDesc, addr.TownshipDir, addr.RangeDir, addr.Validated, addr.PrimaryMeridian, addr.PLSSCounty, addr.AddressHash, addr.GeocodeLevel, addr.GeocodeLevelDescription, addr.Meridian, addr.AddressOverrideInd, addr.DistanceToCoast, addr.DistanceToCoastInd, addr.AddrAliasModifiedInd, addr.Country 
FROM
 addr addr inner join advrxxchangedbeans b
on addr.Systemid=b.Systemid
and addr.CmmContainer=b.CmmContainer
and b.CmmContainer in ('Policy','Claim','Application')
 where concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$m_strtdt' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$m_Enddt'
and ( AddrTypeCd like '%Mailing%'
Or AddrTypeCd like '%Risk%'
Or AddrTypeCd like '%CoverageStreetAddr%')
